## ğŸ”¢ Coefficient System

### Formula
```
Coefficient = 1.60 - ((days_in_band - min_days) Ã— 0.60 / (max_days - min_days))
```

### Rules
- **Most Common Band**: Coefficient = 1.00
- **Rarest Band**: Coefficient = 1.60
- **Inverse Relationship**: Fewer days = Higher coefficient

